</P>
</GRAPHIC>
<TYPE>
<P>
Wild Art 
</P>
</TYPE>
</DOC>
<DOC>
<DOCNO> LA030490-0030 </DOCNO>
<DOCID> 184313 </DOCID>
<DATE>
<P>
March 4, 1990, Sunday, Home Edition 
</P>
</DATE>
<SECTION>
<P>
Calendar; Page 62; Calendar Desk 
</P>
</SECTION>
<GRAPHIC>
<P>
Photo, Mundell Lowe headlines today at Inn L'Auberge, Del Mar. CON KEYES / Loa 
Angeles Times 
</P>
</GRAPHIC>
<TYPE>
<P>
