</P>
</HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
Some of the Soviet-inspired fashion items mentioned in "Bloc Busters" by 
Rose-Marie Turk (Feb. 23) are indications of some very sick minds. 
</P>
<P>
In particular, I am referring to Harvey Russack and his Unique Clothing 
