<P>
THANKS, GREENBERG 
</P>
</HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
I would like to paraphrase the headline of Peter Greenberg's Jan. 21 article 
from "High Praise for a Pilot Who Knew, etc." to "High Praise for a Writer Who 
Knows." 
</P>
<P>
In my years of travel and travel reading, I have never read a person who is 
more knowledgeable than Peter Greenberg. My file cabinets are full of his 
articles, and it's evident that he does much research on whatever he writes 
about. His articles touch on subjects no one else writes about, and are of 
great use to a traveler. 
</P>
<P>
DOROTHY KEARN 
