BOLD WENCH IS NEXT MOVE WINNER 
</P>
</HEADLINE>
<BYLINE>
<P>
By Associated Press 
</P>
</BYLINE>
<DATELINE>
<P>
NEW YORK 
</P>
</DATELINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
Bold Wench led from the start but barely hung on for a half-length victory in 
the $113,800 Next Move Breeders Cup Handicap at Aqueduct on Saturday. 
</P>
</TEXT>
<TYPE>
