COLLEGE NEWS: COUNSELOR AT MT. SAC RECEIVES RECOGNITION 
</P>
</HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
Ed Nettell, a counselor at Mt. San Antonio College in Walnut, is one of five 
California community college employees recognized by the California 
Articulation Number System for his efforts in articulation. 
</P>
<P>
Articulation involves matching community college classes to their equivalents 
in university systems and seeing that student credits at two-year colleges 
transfer to four-year colleges and universities. 
</P>
