<P>
COLLEGE NEWS: PCC WILL TAILOR PROGRAMS TO BUSINESSES 
</P>
</HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
Pasadena City College has created an Economic Development Office that will 
offer customized educational programs to local businesses. 
</P>
<P>
The program will include courses in English as a second language, business and 
intercultural communications, cutting-edge technology, supervisory training, 
and stress management. The classes are provided at the request of the business 
