ISRAEL; ISRAEL -- FOREIGN RELATIONS -- PLO; PALESTINIANS -- ISRAEL; ISRAEL -- 
TERRITORIES AND POSSESSIONS; ISRAEL -- GOVERNMENT 
</P>
