student Irian Diaz enjoy a visit. As part of her studies, Diaz lives and works 
at the facility. ; Photo, After spending the day caring for Kingsley Manor 
residents, Diaz settles down to hit the books. MARIANNA DIAMOS 
</P>
</GRAPHIC>
