March 4, 1990, Sunday, Orange County Edition 
</P>
</DATE>
<P>
THOMAS J MAYS 
</P>
<SECTION>
<P>
Metro; Part B; Page 1; Column 2; Metro Desk 
</P>
</SECTION>
<LENGTH>
