<P>
March 4, 1990, Sunday, Home Edition 
</P>
</DATE>
<P>
BEN DAVIDIAN 
</P>
<SECTION>
<P>
Part A; Page 3; Column 1; Metro Desk 
</P>
</SECTION>
<LENGTH>
